  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bc7\u0b9f \u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Special request to President Ranil",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The report released by the Human Rights Watch has indicated that the promise to repeal the Anti-Terrorism Act and introduce a new law to protect people's rights has been continuously violated.",
        "The Observatory has requested President Ranil Wickremesinghe to immediately stop the crackdown on protesters through the Prevention of Terrorism Act.",
        "The report further stated that the current government has imposed emergency laws and is cracking down on protesters with violence and arrests."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "Ranil",
          "label": "PERSON"
        }
      ],
